v0.1.0-alpha:
  Date: 2015-10-15
      - Alpha release.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

v0.1.1-alpha:
  Date: 2015-10-15
    Changes:
      - Added resize.
      - Fixed default values for grid.
      - Fixed default values for box.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

v0.1.2-alpha:
  Date: 2015-11-22
    Changes:
      - Added updateBox api.
      - Removed box rendering css from css files (now the css file is not
        necessary).
      - Removed box id, now box id is not necessary when inserting boxes.
      - Fixed default values for box.

    Bug fixes:
      - During resizing, when it was close to the bottom of the screen,
        it didn't stop at the inward margin.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

v0.1.3-alpha:
  Date: 2015-12-06
    Changes:
      - Changed how grid height / width / columnWidth / rowHeight is set.
      - Added options of setting rowHeight / columnWidth.
      - Added content element to box (ability to add custom html).

    Bug fixes:
      - Less than 0 rowspan / columnspan fixed.
      - Fixed that boxes went outside border after indirect collision.

    Misc:
      - Added collision tests.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

v0.2.0-alpha:
  Date: 2016-01-15
    Changes:
      - Added drag handle.
      - Faster animations using window.requestAnimationFrame. About 25% better
        performance overall.
      - Added dragstart, dragging, dragend / resizestart, resizing, resize end
        callback events.
      - Added resizeHandle option.
      - Added insert / remove box api.
      - Added handleWidth option.
      - Cleaned up code.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

v0.2.1-alpha:
  Date: 2016-03-19
    Changes:
      - Fixed numRows / numColumns when moving box and on collision.
      - Refactored gridEngine / engineCore / engineView so gridCore only contains
        logic and no graphic calls. Also gridEngine is now a wrapper for
        updateBox and other API.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
